Server Manager → Manage → Add Roles and Features
Server Roles → ✅ Remote Access
Role Services → ✅ Routing → Add Features
Install → дождаться → Close

2 — Настроить RRAS:

Server Manager → Tools → Routing and Remote Access
Правой кнопкой на сервер → Configure and Enable Routing and Remote Access
Next → Custom configuration → Next
✅ LAN routing → Next → Finish
Start Service

3 — Добавить маршрут до ASTA:

RRAS → IPv4 → правой кнопкой Static Routes → New Static Route

Destination: 192.168.128.0
Netmask:     255.255.128.0
Gateway:     20.0.0.1
Metric:      1

OK


